            and developed into an independent project in 2013 in the frame of the PhD of Kevin Darras (Agroecology, University of G&ouml;ttingen), together with Mauladi (Information Systems, University of Jambi). Noemi Perez (freelance web engineer) joined us later and considerably re-designed, re-factored and extended the tool&#39;s capabilities.
            </span>
        </p>
        <p>
            <span>The development was funded by the DFG CRC990 project&#39;s phase 1 and phase 2 grants and supported by the Agroecology research group.</span>
